bilingual.source: SpaceShipTwo is suspended from the middle of the wing.
bilingual.target: 太空船二号悬挂在机翼的中部。

bilingual.source: The hospital's new wing is dedicated to outpatient services.
bilingual.target: 医院的新楼翼专门用于门诊病人服务。

bilingual.source: The library named a wing after its most generous patron.
bilingual.target: 图书馆以其最慷慨的赞助人的名字命名了一翼。

bilingual.source: The debate between left-wing and right-wing policies is ongoing.
bilingual.target: 关于左翼和右翼政策的辩论仍在继续。

list.abstract: wing老游戏常用组件如孔明传，等一系列的95年左右的游戏·
wing是一个英语单词，可以用作名词和动词，可以翻译为翅膀、飞翔，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: Jeff? Pop! I'm okay. I was on the other wing. They brought us to Jersey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 杰夫？老爸，我没事，我在另一边的机翼上，救援人员接我到了新泽西。

yingyinNormal.en: Nothing together. That's all right. Hell, I'll fly on the wing. Here we go. 22A, 6A and 6C.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有连座了。没关系，让我坐机翼都行。票拿好，22排A座，6排A座，还有6排C座。

yingyinNormal.en: Good. Oh, FYI. After I eat my sandwich, I'm taking Koothrappali's Patang kite out for a test run. Would you like to get your delta-wing raptor and join me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 很好，顺便提醒你，我吃完三明治之后，我就带库萨帕里的帕唐风筝出去试飞一下，你想带着你的三角翼猛禽跟我一起去吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Thanks, Frank. Welcome to the West Wing. Thank you, sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢 Frank，欢迎加入白宫。感谢您，总统先生。

yingyinNormal.en: Sell cupcakes at the diabetes wing at the children's hospital?
yingyinNormal.zh: 难不成要去儿童医院。

yingyinNormal.en: Put 'er there! Welcome! Sorry. And a hoof to a wing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 能握个手吗？欢迎你们！抱歉。蹄子握翅膀。

yingyinNormal.en: Rope off across the staircases and the back wing. Who are the guides?
yingyinNormal.zh: 用绳子把楼梯和后屋都拦上，谁做向导？

yingyinNormal.en: In my world, if I'm suspended or expelled, a wing is donated in the Bass name.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我的世界里，如果我被勒令休学或者开除，有栋楼将因拜斯家族的捐助而树起。

yingyinNormal.en: I was a powerless and helpless boy, until a local sensei took me under his wing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我当时是个无依无靠的男孩，直到当地的老师，收留了我。

yingyinNormal.en: Scroll back, please. To just after you lost your wing man. There. Play back, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请往回倒，回到你的僚机被击落的地方，那里，请重放。

yingyinNormal.en: So, yeah, I'm a kid. And I'm also a goofball. And a wing nut. And a Knucklehead McSpazatron.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，我是个孩子。我是个笨蛋，毛头小伙子，是个大笨蛋！

yingyinNormal.en: All right, Philip, tuck the wing tips under the body of the bird and place in a roasting pan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，菲利普，把翅尖塞到火鸡肚子下面，然后放到烤盘上。

yingyinNormal.en: Chicago KSI headquarters is like a fortress. I'm gonna find a way into their top-secret military wing.
yingyinNormal.zh: KSI芝加哥总部就像一座堡垒，我会想办法混入最高军事机密区。

yingyinNormal.en: I drew up plans for a Duckingham Palace, but I can't find them, so I guess we'll just have to "wing" it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我画了好几种鸭金汉宫的修建草图，不过我找不到图纸了，看来我们只能现场发挥[翅膀]了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, really? Did you make a second date? Well, no, we sort of decided to wing it. Oh, even I know that's lame.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的？你俩定了下一次约会吗？这倒没有...我们说好了，到时候再想。得了吧，连我都觉得这太逊了。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone's to keep their feet firmly on the ground while I take Mr. Longbottom to the hospital wing. Understand?
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在大家都老老实实地在地上呆着，我送隆巴顿先生去医院，懂了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I built this whole wing. I kept firing the architects and builders, so no-one knew quite how it all fitted together.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这一区的病房是我建的。建筑师和建筑工人被我开了一个又一个，所以没人知道这儿的整体设计。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. When you walk into the museum, take a right, okay? That's the antiquities wing. Ancient Egypt, Mesopotamia, up to the Byzantine Empire.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你们进入博物馆时，先向右转，那边是古代文物厅，古埃及、美索不达米亚直到拜占庭帝国……

yingyinNormal.en: Master, I just want to assure you that I had no part in this hopeless plan. Preparing a dinner, designing a gown for her, giving her a suite in the east wing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 主人,我只是想向你保证我没参与这悲催的计划。准备晚餐，为她设计礼服，给她一间在东塔的卧室。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. Right! People eat birds. Bird meat. Now do they just fly into your mouth? Or you go in a restaurant and say: Excuse me, I'll have a bucket of fried bird. Or maybe just a wing. Or a…
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，是喔！人类会吃小鸟，小鸟肉，他们是直接飞进你的嘴里吗？ 还是你可以到餐厅说：“不好意思，我要点一份炸鸟”或是一个翅膀，或是…

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: In 1866, the construction of the North <highlight>Wing</highlight> of the Treasury Building necessitated the demolition of the State Department building.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1866年，为了修建财政部大楼北翼，国务院大楼不得不被拆除。

examination_example.sentence: The Navy Department moved into the east <highlight>wing</highlight> in 1879, where elaborate wall and ceiling stenciling and marquetry floors decorated the office of the Secretary.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1879年，海军部搬进了东翼，部长的办公室用了精致的墙壁、天花板模板和镶嵌地板装饰。

examination_example.sentence: Completed in 1875, the State Department's south <highlight>wing</highlight> was the first to be occupied.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 完工于1875年，国务院的南翼是第一个被使用的。

word_usage.usage: wing作动词时，既可作及物动词，又可作不及物动词。作及物动词时，其后可接名词或代词，如：Ambition winged her spirit. 野心激发了她的精神。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 这架混合动力无人机通过使用其固定机翼来保持扫描大片土地的距离和速度。

examination_example.sentence: A little dry and lacking of taste, but at least a <highlight>wing</highlight> didn't get stuck in my throat.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有点干，缺乏味道，但至少一只翅膀没有卡在我的喉咙里。

examination_example.sentence: But all these concepts are massively expensive, require safety certification standards for road and air, need dual controls, involve complex folding <highlight>wings</highlight> and propellers.
